Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住了？
