Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真挺疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我的集章手册被捅了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样危险的事情还是少做吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总算是避免了观众们的恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他更好的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…一下子就
